reviewText: What more can be said about this film?  Loretta Young is still beautiful even in her elder years.  I can't believe I finally found this film on DVD.  I had an old VHS tape which was absolutely horrible quality... very grainy.  This version was much better and I could use the Forward/Backwards buttons to skip to my favorite scenes!  I will be watching this DVD for many Holidays to come!!!
summary: Christmas is here early!  Loretta Young is amazing!

reviewText: This is one of Loretta Young's best pieces of work.  She came out of retirement to make it.  Delightful story, as hers have always been.  Nice Christmas Eve tradition, makes it good to have in one's one personal collection.
